# React patterns

## File roles

- `src/views/**` — page wrappers: breadcrumbs (`BreadcrumbComp`), minimal layout
- `src/components/apps/**` — feature UI; wrap with context provider at top level
- `src/components/ui/**` — shadcn primitives; prefer composition over edits
- `src/components/shared/**` — cross-feature helpers (`CardBox`, etc.)

## Conventions

```tsx
// ✅ View: thin page shell
const Notes = () => (
  <>
    <BreadcrumbComp title="Notes app" items={BCrumb} />
    <NotesApp />
  </>
);

// ✅ Feature root wraps its provider
export default function NotesApp() {
  return (
    <NotesProvider>
      <NotesContent />
    </NotesProvider>
  );
}
```

- Functional components with explicit prop/context interfaces
- Context pattern: `createContext` + provider in `src/context/<feature>/index.tsx`
- Types in `src/types/apps/<feature>.ts`
- Use `FC` or explicit return types consistently with the surrounding file
- No `src/hooks/` folder yet — colocate hooks in feature folders if needed
